Package: shinyelectron
Title: Export Shiny Applications as Desktop Applications using Electron
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("James Joseph", "Balamuta",
            email = "james.balamuta@gmail.com", 
            role = c("aut", "cre"),
            comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2826-8458")
           )
    )
Description: Provides tools to export R or Python Shiny applications as
    standalone desktop applications using Electron. Applications run natively
    on Windows, macOS, and Linux; depending on the runtime strategy chosen,
    end users do not need R or Python installed on their machine.
License: AGPL (>= 3)
URL: https://r-pkg.thecoatlessprofessor.com/shinyelectron/, https://github.com/coatless-rpkg/shinyelectron
